{"id":33698,"type":2,"name":"盛夏十日","summary":"   绝症少年楚辰回到乡下的爷爷家准备静静度过自己不到一个月的余生。\r\n      然而阴差阳错之下他帮助了隐居在人类世界的吸血鬼、狼人、狐妖以及桃木仙。四个不同种族的非人类为了偿还人情决定让楚辰成为成为各自的同族活下去。然而在四个身份中，楚辰的选择只有一个。\r\n      是成为像兰斯一样绅士的吸血鬼，还是化身弗莱斯顿那样强壮的狼人？是作为拥有十足魅力像莫小瑶小姐那样的狐妖延续生命，还是选择变成像慕杨那样气质优雅的桃木仙？\r\n      生与死的界限一瞬间模糊不清，眼前只看到充满刺激与欢乐的日子……\r\n","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>盛夏十日</li><li><span>话数: </span>10</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>??</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://tieba.baidu.com/f?kz=1024670278</li><li><span>制作: </span>SCIA工作室</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":1,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"国产","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":147584,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/147584","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":147585,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/147585","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":147586,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/147586","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":147587,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/147587","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":147588,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/147588","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":147589,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/147589","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":147590,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/147590","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":147591,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/147591","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":147592,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/147592","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":147593,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/147593"